short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Provide additional functionality in Atlassian products

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Provides various improvements to Atlassian apps

If you have something you would like to improve about an app, feel free to PR it or open an issue! https://github.com/Riley19280/atlassian-enhancements

Features:

- Save previously selected repository and branch when creating a branch from GitHub.
- Show a button to copy the command to check out a branch locally after creating it from GitHub.
